WEBVTT

01:38.030 --> 01:40.759
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.289 --> 01:43.560
[Episode 12]

01:44.900 --> 01:46.600
[Chongling Valley]

01:58.509 --> 01:59.240
Who's there?

02:42.470 --> 02:43.190
Found him.

02:57.470 --> 02:57.930
Junior!

02:58.130 --> 02:59.460
What exactly happened?

02:59.480 --> 03:00.190
I rushed to Nine Absolutes Cave

03:00.190 --> 03:01.080
as soon as I got the letter,

03:01.080 --> 03:02.560
but by the time I arrived,
the fight was already over.

03:02.560 --> 03:03.800
How exactly did Li Si die?

03:03.800 --> 03:05.150
Has the missing tablet been found?

03:05.150 --> 03:05.630
Junior,

03:06.150 --> 03:07.470
where are you rushing off to?

03:07.470 --> 03:08.000
Junior!

03:11.280 --> 03:12.150
Young Sect Master,

03:12.150 --> 03:13.680
are we still following her?

03:17.520 --> 03:17.960
Yes.

03:29.079 --> 03:31.900
[Qingsheng Residence]

03:30.360 --> 03:31.370
Master is meditating

03:31.370 --> 03:32.970
and not receiving visitors.

03:36.030 --> 03:36.690
Move aside!

03:47.520 --> 03:48.400
Who let you in?

03:48.680 --> 03:50.140
My master is in seclusion.

03:51.150 --> 03:52.210
Junior, after you.

03:53.280 --> 03:54.810
What's wrong with you guys?

04:15.480 --> 04:16.519
He's dead?

04:41.510 --> 04:42.510
Don't waste time.

04:43.270 --> 04:44.710
Just come at us all at once.

04:44.710 --> 04:47.080
[Mingzhu House]

05:00.630 --> 05:01.390
How is she?

05:01.950 --> 05:03.510
Miss Lyu was badly frightened earlier,

05:03.510 --> 05:04.360
and her heart condition flared up.

05:04.360 --> 05:06.390
She just took some medicine
and has fallen asleep.

05:06.390 --> 05:07.430
I'd like to see her.

05:07.430 --> 05:08.920
Be quiet. Don't wake her.

05:22.000 --> 05:24.000
With skills like that,
they actually dared to chase us?

05:24.000 --> 05:26.530
They really had no idea
what we're capable of.

05:30.120 --> 05:30.920
What's wrong?

05:31.160 --> 05:32.890
Is the medicine taking effect?

05:33.190 --> 05:33.990
Seems like it.

05:34.430 --> 05:36.040
Then we need to find a place
to rest quickly.

05:36.040 --> 05:38.840
Once night falls,
it'll be even more troublesome.

05:55.870 --> 05:57.870
Huai Qing said you had gone to sleep.

06:00.560 --> 06:01.830
My mind is unsettled.

06:02.480 --> 06:03.390
I can't sleep.

06:14.720 --> 06:16.800
"The horses raise their hooves
and neigh in sorrow.

06:16.800 --> 06:18.750
Flags wave, and the sound of drums
shakes the sky.

06:18.750 --> 06:20.550
Sharp blades meet the front line

06:20.560 --> 06:22.480
as urgent military dispatches
arrive in haste.

06:22.480 --> 06:24.190
This body is not worth sparing—

06:24.190 --> 06:26.240
what matters is to answer
the nation's peril.

06:26.240 --> 06:28.160
We ride deep into the enemy lines
without hesitation.

06:28.160 --> 06:30.160
If sacrifice is demanded, so be it."

06:31.680 --> 06:32.740
Did you write this?

06:35.630 --> 06:37.040
It was Mr. Li who wrote it.

06:42.270 --> 06:43.400
Don't overthink it.

06:43.870 --> 06:44.560
Dr. Zhu

06:44.870 --> 06:46.870
will definitely cure your illness.

06:49.600 --> 06:51.560
I just can't figure it out.

06:52.000 --> 06:52.930
Figure out what?

06:55.190 --> 06:56.000
Mei,

06:56.560 --> 06:58.390
could someone who writes such poetry

06:58.390 --> 06:59.650
really be a bad person?

07:00.430 --> 07:02.830
Could he be someone who seeks immortality?

07:14.750 --> 07:15.550
Immortal Xin.

07:16.160 --> 07:17.090
Why are you here?

07:17.750 --> 07:18.950
Just making a living.

07:19.070 --> 07:21.070
I've got to know a bit of everything.

07:21.750 --> 07:23.000
I'm just here to see him.

07:23.000 --> 07:23.800
Don't mind me.

07:27.070 --> 07:29.730
The heavens are vast
and the earth is boundless.

07:29.920 --> 07:33.430
May you have good fortune, wealth,
and prosperity in all things.

07:33.430 --> 07:35.690
Now that you've set out, do not look back.

07:36.000 --> 07:39.930
On the road to the southwest,
there's a guiding light from the heavens.

07:50.830 --> 07:53.690
Immortal Xin, you are not from
around here, are you?

07:55.240 --> 07:57.159
We have a custom here:

07:58.270 --> 08:00.160
when someone dies,
you have to call out to their grave,

08:00.160 --> 08:02.490
scattering joss paper while calling out.

08:02.630 --> 08:03.680
Like you just did?

08:04.270 --> 08:04.830
Yes.

08:05.270 --> 08:06.270
Legend has it that

08:06.680 --> 08:08.210
at the turn of day and night,

08:08.560 --> 08:10.360
if one keeps walking southwest—

08:10.720 --> 08:12.000
not turning back at mountains

08:12.000 --> 08:13.510
and not detouring when meeting rivers—

08:13.510 --> 08:14.360
one can reach

08:14.360 --> 08:16.160
the place where immortals live.

08:16.160 --> 08:16.950
There, the paths are paved

08:16.950 --> 08:17.830
with gold,

08:18.160 --> 08:19.950
the rivers flow with fine wine,

08:20.940 --> 08:21.560
and the carts are not drawn

08:21.560 --> 08:22.620
by mules or horses,

08:22.680 --> 08:23.740
nor even by humans,

08:23.950 --> 08:25.550
but by celestial phoenixes.

08:25.750 --> 08:28.040
Across the mountains and fields
grow endless ears of grain,

08:28.040 --> 08:31.100
which yield abundant harvests
even without watering.

08:31.560 --> 08:32.960
The immortals don't need gold,

08:32.960 --> 08:34.220
nor do they need to eat.

08:34.270 --> 08:35.360
With a wave of the hand
they summon clouds,

08:35.360 --> 08:36.669
and with a turn of the palm
they bring rain.

08:36.669 --> 08:38.909
A journey of 1,000 li
takes but an instant.

08:38.909 --> 08:40.909
Besides, they live in the heavens,

08:41.270 --> 08:44.000
so you can't really find them
by going southwest.

08:44.720 --> 08:46.120
That's why it's a legend.

08:46.600 --> 08:47.930
These folktales are all

08:48.000 --> 08:49.670
things ordinary people make up themselves.

08:49.670 --> 08:51.240
They shout whatever comes to mind,

08:51.240 --> 08:52.510
and after shouting it out,

08:52.510 --> 08:54.710
it feels as if they've truly gone there.

08:57.320 --> 08:59.320
Actually, Li Si was a decent person.

08:59.720 --> 09:01.440
If he hadn't been confused for a moment,

09:01.440 --> 09:03.170
he wouldn't have lost his life.

09:03.840 --> 09:04.510
I remember you guys

09:04.510 --> 09:06.320
came to Chongling Valley together, right?

09:06.320 --> 09:07.320
Were you friends?

09:07.870 --> 09:08.800
Kind of, I guess.

09:11.120 --> 09:11.650
Alright.

09:12.000 --> 09:12.860
How about this?

09:13.240 --> 09:14.480
You give me a bit more money,

09:14.480 --> 09:15.870
and I'll shout some auspicious words

09:15.870 --> 09:18.470
so he can go on his way
smoothly and peacefully.

09:22.600 --> 09:23.600
Then take this.

09:24.390 --> 09:25.720
This is enough. Enough.

09:28.910 --> 09:29.630
Warrior Li,

09:30.000 --> 09:31.120
look ahead!

09:32.000 --> 09:34.330
The road to the southwest
is flat and wide.

09:34.870 --> 09:38.130
Immortal terraces and pavilions
rise in countless tiers.

09:38.790 --> 09:41.750
There's no illness, no suffering,
and no pain.

09:42.510 --> 09:47.030
Granaries stand full,
and the fields are heavy with grain.

10:01.910 --> 10:03.170
You're finally awake.

10:03.510 --> 10:05.440
You've been asleep for a whole day.

10:05.440 --> 10:06.270
Where am I?

10:06.750 --> 10:08.790
The medicine took effect, and you fainted.

10:08.790 --> 10:10.750
I carried you on my back for a full 2 li

10:10.750 --> 10:12.000
before I finally found

10:12.000 --> 10:12.840
this kind household

10:12.840 --> 10:13.870
who was willing to take us in.

10:13.870 --> 10:15.360
Let's rest for a couple of days
before we get back on the road.

10:15.360 --> 10:16.550
It's not safe in the valley.

10:16.550 --> 10:18.610
I need to get back as soon as possible.

10:20.960 --> 10:23.220
So it's because you missed Immortal Xin.

10:24.840 --> 10:25.370
Alright.

10:26.040 --> 10:27.670
Once you've got someone you care about,

10:27.670 --> 10:28.790
you really do become different.

10:28.790 --> 10:30.150
One day, when you get married

10:30.150 --> 10:32.610
and have someone
who truly understands you,

10:33.150 --> 10:34.480
you won't need my company anymore.

10:34.480 --> 10:36.740
I can then step aside and retire in peace.

10:52.240 --> 10:54.790
Gentleman from the Central Plains,
you are awake.

10:54.790 --> 10:55.650
We're leaving.

10:55.870 --> 10:57.750
Thanks for the care.
Just a small token of appreciation.

10:57.750 --> 10:58.210
This...

10:58.550 --> 10:59.480
This is too much.

10:59.840 --> 11:01.100
Wait here for a moment.

11:04.240 --> 11:05.080
Gentlemen!

11:05.670 --> 11:06.330
Gentlemen!

11:06.840 --> 11:08.170
Please have some fruit.

11:09.750 --> 11:10.240
No need,

11:10.480 --> 11:11.080
thank you.

11:11.480 --> 11:13.010
Alright, I'll give it a try.

11:14.840 --> 11:16.640
You are from the Central Plains?

11:17.240 --> 11:17.670
Yes.

11:18.030 --> 11:19.840
I like people from the Central Plains.

11:19.840 --> 11:21.630
When you come by to rest and have tea,

11:21.630 --> 11:23.490
you give us a lot of food and cloth,

11:23.720 --> 11:24.650
and even sweets.

11:24.720 --> 11:25.980
I like sweets the most.

11:28.200 --> 11:29.330
Where is your sword?

11:29.870 --> 11:30.320
Sword?

11:30.550 --> 11:32.430
People from the Central Plains
are all martial heroes—

11:32.430 --> 11:34.320
always carrying long swords
at their waists,

11:34.320 --> 11:35.320
very impressive.

11:35.750 --> 11:36.670
When I grow up,

11:37.120 --> 11:38.240
I also want to go to the Central Plains

11:38.240 --> 11:39.640
to learn swordsmanship.

11:46.960 --> 11:48.840
This kind of long sword doesn't suit you.

11:48.840 --> 11:49.320
Here,

11:49.790 --> 11:51.050
this suits you better.

11:53.910 --> 11:54.640
Thanks a lot.

11:57.840 --> 11:58.970
Thank you very much.

11:59.080 --> 11:59.960
This is for you guys.

11:59.960 --> 12:00.620
Tea leaves,

12:00.910 --> 12:01.910
refreshing and thirst-quenching.

12:01.910 --> 12:03.270
You can drink it on the way.

12:03.270 --> 12:03.870
Thank you.

12:05.240 --> 12:05.840
Thank you.

12:08.110 --> 12:10.770
That way is the direction
to the Central Plains.

12:11.390 --> 12:12.440
Everyone, come on in.

12:12.440 --> 12:13.440
Hurry up. Come on.

12:14.630 --> 12:15.550
You've had a long journey.

12:15.550 --> 12:16.680
Please come inside.

12:17.000 --> 12:18.320
Guests have arrived. Quick, bring the tea.

12:18.320 --> 12:18.750
Got it.

12:19.120 --> 12:20.720
Please come inside. Please.

12:21.750 --> 12:22.880
Please come inside.

12:23.120 --> 12:23.580
Please.

12:30.390 --> 12:30.920
Let's go.

12:31.080 --> 12:31.610
Let's go.

12:36.150 --> 12:37.910
The medicine has already taken effect.

12:37.910 --> 12:39.280
I assume that when we get back,

12:39.280 --> 12:40.000
Su Taiyi will be able to

12:40.000 --> 12:41.200
renew my bones for me.

12:42.360 --> 12:43.910
With me in Chongling Valley,

12:43.910 --> 12:45.710
you don't need to go back with me.

12:45.730 --> 12:47.390
Go find something for me instead.

12:47.390 --> 12:48.000
What is it?

12:49.570 --> 12:50.480
After bone renewal

12:50.480 --> 12:51.680
comes blood renewal.

12:52.390 --> 12:53.990
I once read in an ancient book

12:54.510 --> 12:56.910
that there's a magical artifact
abandoned by deities

12:56.910 --> 12:58.840
that can be used for blood renewal.

12:58.870 --> 13:01.200
A magical artifact belonging to deities?

13:01.630 --> 13:03.030
Even if it really exists,

13:03.080 --> 13:03.670
it's probably already been

13:03.670 --> 13:05.200
occupied by the Youhu Clan.

13:06.270 --> 13:06.800
Alright.

13:07.320 --> 13:09.320
I'll make a trip to Fangwai Mountain

13:09.360 --> 13:10.030
for you.

13:10.840 --> 13:11.240
Okay.

13:24.600 --> 13:26.750
Another group of immortal sect disciples?

13:26.750 --> 13:27.670
Are they also going there

13:27.670 --> 13:28.390
for tea?

13:31.390 --> 13:32.190
What's wrong?

13:32.840 --> 13:33.640
Let's go back.

14:24.480 --> 14:25.550
Hand over the jade tablet,

14:25.550 --> 14:27.010
and we'll spare your life.

14:28.670 --> 14:30.630
You killed my senior and junior brothers,

14:30.630 --> 14:33.150
yet you expect me to hand over
the Gongshan Jade Tablet?

14:33.150 --> 14:34.010
In your dreams!

14:57.000 --> 14:57.660
Senior Bai.

14:58.390 --> 15:00.550
Here are the lychee pastries from Lingnan.

15:00.550 --> 15:01.610
As you instructed,

15:01.670 --> 15:03.510
they are all made with Lingnan lychees.

15:03.510 --> 15:05.240
I personally watched the shop owner
pick them,

15:05.240 --> 15:07.040
so I guarantee each one is juicy.

15:08.110 --> 15:08.910
This whole journey—

15:08.910 --> 15:10.000
first by carriage,

15:10.000 --> 15:10.730
then by boat—

15:10.750 --> 15:11.720
was anything but easy.

15:11.720 --> 15:12.650
But don't worry,

15:12.680 --> 15:13.670
I wrapped them all carefully

15:13.670 --> 15:14.800
in oil paper for you,

15:14.840 --> 15:17.170
so not a single lychee's skin was damaged.

15:17.720 --> 15:19.150
Thank you for your hard work.

15:19.150 --> 15:20.550
Next time you need anything done,
come to me again.

15:20.550 --> 15:23.810
I guarantee good work, few complications,
and low prices.

15:43.000 --> 15:44.300
This is exactly the taste.

15:44.300 --> 15:46.030
I didn't expect you to still remember it,
Senior.

15:46.030 --> 15:47.830
Where did you buy these, Senior?

15:48.030 --> 15:49.260
A friend wrote to me a few days ago,

15:49.260 --> 15:50.320
saying he was traveling south
along the Yangtze River

15:50.320 --> 15:51.200
to tour the Yong region

15:51.200 --> 15:52.840
and would happen to pass through
Chongling Valley.

15:52.840 --> 15:54.120
So I asked him to bring some pastries

15:54.120 --> 15:55.840
from Tianyuan Mountain for you to try.

15:55.840 --> 15:57.440
That's really thoughtful of you, Senior.

15:57.440 --> 15:58.510
We are fellow disciples.

15:58.510 --> 15:59.510
Don't mention it.

16:03.960 --> 16:05.750
Tianyuan Sect and Xin Xie Manor

16:06.120 --> 16:07.380
share the same origin.

16:07.920 --> 16:08.790
Back then, it was because
Senior Uncle Xin Xiong

16:08.790 --> 16:10.190
had a dispute with Master

16:10.200 --> 16:11.730
that he took you away from Tianyuan Sect

16:11.730 --> 16:12.630
to establish a new sect.

16:12.630 --> 16:13.490
Over the years,

16:13.630 --> 16:14.840
the two sects haven't interacted much,

16:14.840 --> 16:16.000
so we've indeed grown somewhat distant.

16:16.000 --> 16:16.800
But it's okay.

16:16.980 --> 16:17.930
Junior, if you

16:17.960 --> 16:19.120
encounter any difficulties in the valley,

16:19.120 --> 16:20.650
feel free to ask me for help.

16:20.750 --> 16:21.860
Rest assured, Senior Brother.

16:21.860 --> 16:23.390
I won't hesitate to ask you.

16:25.120 --> 16:25.720
By the way,

16:26.440 --> 16:27.390
was that senior expert next to you

16:27.390 --> 16:28.960
in the dining hall that day

16:29.320 --> 16:31.320
sent by Senior Uncle to protect you?

16:32.200 --> 16:33.800
He's from Chongling Valley.

16:33.870 --> 16:35.200
From Chongling Valley?

16:36.030 --> 16:36.560
A doctor?

16:36.870 --> 16:38.200
I don't know about that.

16:38.550 --> 16:40.010
Mr. Lu is very impressive.

16:40.270 --> 16:41.550
His magical powers are superb,

16:41.550 --> 16:43.550
he paints ink paintings beautifully,

16:43.550 --> 16:44.790
and he knows a bit of medicine.

16:44.790 --> 16:47.120
It seems there's nothing
he doesn't know how to do.

16:47.120 --> 16:48.840
When I first entered the valley,

16:48.840 --> 16:49.510
I fell so ill

16:49.840 --> 16:51.120
that I couldn't even drink water
without vomiting.

16:51.120 --> 16:52.320
I almost lost my life.

16:52.910 --> 16:54.310
It was Mr. Lu who saved me.

16:54.720 --> 16:56.600
Not only did he take great care of me,

16:56.600 --> 16:58.550
but he also taught me
the Fish Drinking Technique.

16:58.550 --> 16:59.270
So,

16:59.320 --> 17:00.960
you two first met in the valley?

17:00.960 --> 17:01.390
Yes.

17:01.630 --> 17:02.870
And the very first time you met,

17:02.870 --> 17:04.599
he was already that kind to you?

17:04.790 --> 17:06.349
Mr. Lu doesn't put on airs.

17:06.750 --> 17:08.010
He's kind to everyone.

17:11.550 --> 17:13.210
An extraordinary man indeed.

17:25.400 --> 17:26.240
Divine Doctor Su.

17:26.240 --> 17:27.170
Why are you here?

17:28.030 --> 17:29.490
I came to visit Junior Xin.

17:30.650 --> 17:32.240
Your Tianyuan Sect and the Xin Xie Manor

17:32.240 --> 17:33.110
split long ago.

17:33.640 --> 17:35.270
She has nothing to do with you.

17:35.270 --> 17:36.830
Calling her "Junior" like that—

17:36.830 --> 17:38.430
how affectionate you sound.

17:39.960 --> 17:41.750
All disciples of the immortal sects
are one family.

17:41.750 --> 17:42.830
There's no distinction between us.

17:42.830 --> 17:43.760
No distinction?

17:44.690 --> 17:45.820
Then how about I take your Tianyuan Sect's

17:45.820 --> 17:46.750
Immortality Pills
and distribute them to others?

17:46.750 --> 17:48.010
Would that be alright?

17:50.590 --> 17:51.850
Don't come here again.

17:52.030 --> 17:54.310
Our Nine Absolutes Cave
is a forbidden area.

17:54.310 --> 17:55.590
This Xieyun Cottage

17:56.070 --> 17:57.600
is a forbidden area as well.

18:00.880 --> 18:01.880
Divine Doctor Su.

18:02.030 --> 18:03.920
The last time Senior Bai went to
Nine Absolutes Cave

18:03.920 --> 18:04.960
was to save you.

18:05.880 --> 18:07.340
Let him speak for himself.

18:07.720 --> 18:09.600
It was true that I broke the rules
last time,

18:09.600 --> 18:10.270
but it was also true

18:10.270 --> 18:12.160
that I worried about your safety,
Divine Doctor.

18:12.160 --> 18:14.110
Oh? So you can predict the future

18:14.270 --> 18:16.130
and knew I'd be in danger that day?

18:16.130 --> 18:17.220
Or are your eyes

18:17.250 --> 18:18.810
always watching our Chongling Valley,

18:18.810 --> 18:19.680
so even the slightest movement

18:19.680 --> 18:21.340
couldn't escape your notice?

18:23.200 --> 18:24.400
The sun is scorching today,

18:24.400 --> 18:25.440
so your temper is flaring, Divine Doctor.

18:25.440 --> 18:26.590
I'll come visit again

18:26.590 --> 18:27.510
some other time.

18:27.510 --> 18:29.040
Don't bother coming again.

18:37.110 --> 18:38.170
Looking so shifty,

18:38.590 --> 18:40.680
he's obviously not a good person.

18:45.310 --> 18:46.510
If you need anything,

18:46.640 --> 18:47.840
just tell Changshou.

18:48.400 --> 18:49.790
Make yourself at home here.

18:49.790 --> 18:51.390
No need to feel constrained.

18:51.550 --> 18:53.010
Thank you, Divine Doctor.

18:56.550 --> 18:57.960
By the way, Divine Doctor,

18:57.960 --> 19:00.160
I was under a Spell of Utterance before,

19:00.750 --> 19:02.270
and I'd throw up whenever I drank water.

19:02.270 --> 19:04.590
But I suddenly recovered that day.

19:05.160 --> 19:05.960
I could eat and drink

19:05.960 --> 19:06.890
normally again.

19:07.440 --> 19:08.030
Divine Doctor, could you

19:08.030 --> 19:09.160
take my pulse and see

19:09.350 --> 19:10.750
what exactly is going on?

19:10.790 --> 19:12.190
You recovered suddenly?

19:14.510 --> 19:16.680
Then there's no need to take your pulse.

19:16.680 --> 19:18.510
So you know how I recovered,
Divine Doctor?

19:18.510 --> 19:19.550
How else?

19:19.790 --> 19:21.320
It must have been pure luck.

19:21.590 --> 19:22.790
Don't overthink it.

19:23.000 --> 19:24.590
When Lu Qianqiao comes back,

19:24.590 --> 19:25.510
he will tell you

19:25.680 --> 19:27.210
exactly how you recovered.

19:31.070 --> 19:31.750
Xin Mei.

19:32.510 --> 19:33.910
How old are you this year?

19:34.590 --> 19:37.390
Are your parents and other relatives
still alive?

19:37.480 --> 19:39.210
When do you plan to get married?

19:41.110 --> 19:42.040
Senior,

19:42.070 --> 19:44.200
why are you asking this out of the blue?

19:45.110 --> 19:46.680
You're a good girl.

19:46.950 --> 19:48.510
The more I look at you,
the more I like you,

19:48.510 --> 19:50.710
so I wanted to show some concern for you.

19:51.920 --> 19:52.520
By the way,

19:53.400 --> 19:54.790
all the other sects

19:54.880 --> 19:56.320
came in groups

19:56.350 --> 19:57.550
of fellow disciples.

19:57.680 --> 19:58.880
Why is it that your sect

19:58.880 --> 20:00.110
sent you here alone?

20:00.310 --> 20:01.480
Where is your master?

20:01.480 --> 20:03.480
Isn't he helping you?

20:04.350 --> 20:05.200
My master

20:05.960 --> 20:08.220
doesn't know I came to Chongling Valley.

20:08.510 --> 20:09.070
Got it.

20:09.480 --> 20:10.540
So you sneaked out.

20:13.110 --> 20:14.400
In truth, it's because

20:14.680 --> 20:16.400
the Jianmu Heavenly Ladder was destroyed,

20:16.400 --> 20:18.790
and ascension for humans
is now impossible.

20:18.790 --> 20:21.590
My master is
a Great Completion Realm cultivator.

20:21.920 --> 20:24.110
Though he never had an obsession
with becoming a deity,

20:24.110 --> 20:25.710
without a goal to strive for,

20:25.880 --> 20:27.590
his moral sense has become unstable

20:27.590 --> 20:29.590
and his cultivation has stagnated.

20:30.480 --> 20:32.830
Now his lifespan is nearing its end.

20:33.720 --> 20:36.050
I'm afraid he doesn't have much time left.

20:39.000 --> 20:40.590
That's why I came here this time

20:40.590 --> 20:41.880
without telling him—

20:42.750 --> 20:44.440
I wanted to use the jade tablet
to exchange for the elixir

20:44.440 --> 20:45.970
to extend my master's life.

20:46.310 --> 20:47.840
But now, the tablet's gone.

20:48.890 --> 20:50.290
I've ruined everything.

20:52.160 --> 20:53.400
Have you ever thought about

20:53.400 --> 20:54.920
why your master hasn't

20:55.400 --> 20:56.750
come to get the elixir himself

20:56.750 --> 20:58.080
even though he's dying?

21:06.070 --> 21:07.750
I've met Xin Xiong

21:08.030 --> 21:09.310
a few times before.

21:11.910 --> 21:13.230
Your master—

21:13.440 --> 21:15.550
he's hotheaded
and a bit rough around the edges,

21:15.550 --> 21:17.350
but he's upright and honorable.

21:18.350 --> 21:20.200
He did me a great favor back then,

21:20.680 --> 21:23.350
so I offered to give him
the Gongshan Jade Tablet.

21:23.350 --> 21:24.550
Who would have thought

21:24.550 --> 21:25.920
that he not only refused it,

21:25.920 --> 21:27.180
but nearly smashed it.

21:29.450 --> 21:30.210
In the end,

21:30.240 --> 21:31.970
I had to shamelessly pester him

21:32.030 --> 21:34.030
before he reluctantly accepted it.

21:37.960 --> 21:39.000
You're filial,

21:40.720 --> 21:43.250
wanting to seek immortality
for your master.

21:44.160 --> 21:45.890
But have you ever thought about

21:46.110 --> 21:47.170
whether he himself

21:48.070 --> 21:49.730
actually wants immortality?

22:00.270 --> 22:01.590
Can't you just find a place

22:01.590 --> 22:02.590
to sit for a while?

22:02.590 --> 22:03.960
Cai En is dead,
and the jade tablet is gone.

22:03.960 --> 22:05.750
How can you still be so calm,
Young Sect Master?

22:05.750 --> 22:06.950
What do you mean gone?

22:07.400 --> 22:08.070
The Gongshan Jade Tablet

22:08.070 --> 22:09.920
had never been in our hands to begin with.

22:09.920 --> 22:10.550
Li Si,

22:10.680 --> 22:11.480
Xin Xie Manor,

22:11.750 --> 22:12.610
and that Cai En—

22:13.350 --> 22:14.440
they each had

22:14.920 --> 22:16.680
one of the Gongshan Jade Tablets.

22:16.680 --> 22:17.590
Now that they're lost—

22:17.590 --> 22:18.640
you know what it's called?

22:18.640 --> 22:21.160
It's called
"gathering the scattered into one."

22:21.160 --> 22:21.640
It's just that they went

22:21.640 --> 22:23.040
from the hands of 3 people

22:23.200 --> 22:24.800
into the hands of one person.

22:25.200 --> 22:26.930
Young Sect Master, you mean...

22:27.680 --> 22:29.750
As long as we find
the person who killed Cai En,

22:29.750 --> 22:31.920
we can recover all 3 jade tablets at once.

22:31.920 --> 22:32.880
Actually, this might even be better.

22:32.880 --> 22:35.000
It saves me from having to search for them
one by one.

22:35.000 --> 22:36.750
Anyone who wasn't outside
Nine Absolutes Cave that day

22:36.750 --> 22:37.350
could be the murderer

22:37.350 --> 22:38.400
who killed Cai En.

22:38.790 --> 22:40.310
We are naturally innocent.

22:40.310 --> 22:41.440
That person from Xin Xie Manor

22:41.440 --> 22:42.570
went there with you,

22:42.830 --> 22:44.830
so presumably he isn't a suspect either.

22:44.830 --> 22:46.070
There was also Bai Zongying.

22:46.070 --> 22:48.800
He was also outside
Nine Absolutes Cave that day.

22:50.070 --> 22:51.440
Bai Zongying?

22:54.070 --> 22:55.470
I'm not so sure about him.

22:59.500 --> 23:00.440
Those two have no idea of

23:00.440 --> 23:01.770
Senior's whereabouts.

23:02.960 --> 23:04.310
Senior was rescued.

23:05.160 --> 23:06.030
If she's safe,

23:06.350 --> 23:08.110
she should have returned to the sect.

23:08.110 --> 23:10.000
Could it be that we took different paths

23:10.000 --> 23:11.730
and didn't run into each other?

23:11.750 --> 23:13.530
My daughter has been poisoned
by snake venom

23:13.530 --> 23:14.160
and urgently needs

23:14.160 --> 23:16.000
a high-grade Ghost Needle Lotus
for detoxification.

23:16.000 --> 23:17.400
Could someone please have mercy

23:17.400 --> 23:18.880
and save my daughter?

23:19.550 --> 23:20.110
Miss.

23:20.590 --> 23:22.190
Miss, please save her. Mi...

23:31.960 --> 23:33.240
So it's fake.

23:34.110 --> 23:35.970
What are you talking about, Miss?

23:36.070 --> 23:38.270
It was you who poisoned her yourselves,

23:38.440 --> 23:39.040
wasn't it?

23:40.350 --> 23:42.400
We have no idea what you're talking about.

23:42.400 --> 23:42.930
Lianxin!

23:42.970 --> 23:44.500
Lianxin! Wake up, Lianxin.

23:46.510 --> 23:47.110
Darling!

23:47.110 --> 23:47.640
Father!

23:48.400 --> 23:49.550
-Darling!
-Father!

23:49.590 --> 23:50.440
Darling!

24:00.640 --> 24:01.680
It's you again.

24:02.070 --> 24:03.600
Let's talk somewhere else.

24:32.590 --> 24:34.110
Why don't you think about it carefully?

24:34.110 --> 24:35.750
This place is full of Ghost Needle Lotus,

24:35.750 --> 24:37.510
so why would they still beg for medicine?

24:37.510 --> 24:38.510
Enough nonsense.

24:38.590 --> 24:39.480
Gentleman!

24:39.880 --> 24:40.790
Gentleman!

24:43.720 --> 24:44.450
Are you okay?

24:45.000 --> 24:45.600
Come here.

25:04.680 --> 25:05.590
Here, Lianxin.

25:06.200 --> 25:07.830
Careful, it's hot.

25:08.680 --> 25:09.340
Be careful.

25:09.550 --> 25:11.590
They've been herb farmers for generations,

25:11.590 --> 25:12.640
making a living

25:12.680 --> 25:13.680
by growing herbs.

25:15.070 --> 25:16.720
Now that the heavenly ladder
has been severed,

25:16.720 --> 25:18.680
the immortal sects are trying to
achieve immortality

25:18.680 --> 25:20.110
through pills and elixirs.

25:20.110 --> 25:21.480
Chongling Valley wants to refine elixirs,

25:21.480 --> 25:23.000
and the court demands medicinal supplies,

25:23.000 --> 25:24.460
so they've set up a pretext

25:24.680 --> 25:26.750
and imposed an "Immortality Tax"
on these herb farmers.

25:26.750 --> 25:27.750
Coincidentally,

25:27.920 --> 25:29.720
the Ghost Needle Lotus they grow

25:29.960 --> 25:30.830
is one of the spiritual herbs

25:30.830 --> 25:32.090
used for making pills.

25:32.680 --> 25:33.830
The Ghost Needle Lotus

25:33.830 --> 25:35.690
is nourished by heaven and earth.

25:35.880 --> 25:37.350
Two inches is considered low-grade,

25:37.350 --> 25:38.680
5 inches medium-grade,

25:39.160 --> 25:40.680
and only when it grows to 10 inches

25:40.680 --> 25:41.920
can it produce a needle lotus,

25:41.920 --> 25:43.520
which counts as high-grade.

25:43.640 --> 25:46.480
To refine the Immortality Pills,
the requirements are extremely strict—

25:46.480 --> 25:48.340
only high-grade ones are usable.

25:48.840 --> 25:50.310
So they poisoned their own children

25:50.310 --> 25:51.310
with snake venom,

25:51.830 --> 25:52.960
not to extort money,

25:53.310 --> 25:54.440
but to pay the tax?

25:58.670 --> 25:59.330
Taste this.

26:02.350 --> 26:03.880
Their water supply has gone bad.

26:03.880 --> 26:05.210
It's bitter and astringent,

26:05.210 --> 26:05.920
so it can't irrigate

26:05.920 --> 26:08.550
Ghost Needle Lotus
that meets the required standards.

26:08.550 --> 26:09.810
That's their problem.

26:11.160 --> 26:12.690
But when you think about it,

26:13.940 --> 26:14.640
isn't their problem also,

26:14.640 --> 26:16.570
in a sense, this family's problem?

26:17.310 --> 26:19.640
The Immortality Tax carries
collective punishment.

26:19.640 --> 26:20.770
If they can't pay it,

26:21.030 --> 26:22.960
the whole family will be forced into
hard labor—

26:22.960 --> 26:24.620
even the kid cannot escape it.

26:25.240 --> 26:26.970
They truly had no other option,

26:27.200 --> 26:29.920
so they had to resort to scam
in front of a pharmacy.

26:29.920 --> 26:30.790
There are only a few

26:30.790 --> 26:32.000
pharmacies in town.

26:32.590 --> 26:34.790
How many times could they possibly
get away with it?

26:34.790 --> 26:36.440
The pharmacy owners aren't their target.

26:36.440 --> 26:38.370
They're after passersby like you.

26:38.590 --> 26:40.240
The pharmacies know their situation,

26:40.240 --> 26:41.700
so they won't expose them.

26:43.270 --> 26:44.830
What a pretentious excuse.

26:45.510 --> 26:46.640
If that was the case,

26:46.690 --> 26:47.690
why didn't they

26:47.720 --> 26:48.920
poison themselves with snake venom

26:48.920 --> 26:50.720
instead of doing it to their kid?

26:52.680 --> 26:53.610
Times are tough.

26:54.200 --> 26:55.180
People's hearts

26:55.380 --> 26:57.110
have grown colder than before.

26:57.490 --> 26:59.440
A child can still win a bit of sympathy—

26:59.440 --> 27:00.680
if it were an adult,

27:01.350 --> 27:04.010
most would likely
just ignore them altogether.

27:42.200 --> 27:43.930
Why are you still following me?

27:44.030 --> 27:46.160
This is the only way out of the village.

27:50.520 --> 27:51.720
It is said that Tianyin Mountain

27:51.720 --> 27:53.380
is a prominent immortal sect,

27:53.510 --> 27:55.110
best at expounding doctrines

27:55.110 --> 27:56.370
and resolving doubts.

27:56.880 --> 27:57.830
I happen to have a question

27:57.830 --> 27:59.230
I'd like to ask you about.

28:00.270 --> 28:01.530
Please go ahead, Miss.

28:01.750 --> 28:04.030
What is the path of your Tianyin Mountain?

28:04.030 --> 28:05.270
The Path of Severing Emotions.

28:05.270 --> 28:07.030
What is the Path of Severing Emotions?

28:07.030 --> 28:08.310
The great path is emotionless.

28:08.310 --> 28:09.840
It gives rise to all things.

28:09.960 --> 28:11.550
The sun and moon revolve beyond it,

28:11.550 --> 28:13.440
while day and night alternate within it—

28:13.440 --> 28:14.270
unceasing

28:14.830 --> 28:16.160
and without deviation.

28:16.750 --> 28:18.350
It is so because there are
no personal feelings in the heart,

28:18.350 --> 28:19.880
and no favoritism in action.

28:19.880 --> 28:20.880
All living beings

28:21.680 --> 28:23.200
and all things are like dust in our eyes—

28:23.200 --> 28:23.830
that is

28:24.590 --> 28:26.320
the Path of Severing Emotions.

28:27.710 --> 28:28.890
Then what is it that your master

28:28.890 --> 28:29.790
sent you down the mountain to find?

28:29.790 --> 28:30.590
To find my path

28:31.030 --> 28:32.030
and overcome my tribulation.

28:32.030 --> 28:32.830
That's not it.

28:34.350 --> 28:36.280
It should be to find your emotions.

28:36.830 --> 28:38.490
You were born extraordinary,

28:38.640 --> 28:39.960
with exceptional immortal perception.

28:39.960 --> 28:40.920
From a young age,

28:41.460 --> 28:42.830
you knew that in 20 years,

28:42.830 --> 28:44.490
all your loved ones would die.

28:44.680 --> 28:46.940
Have you ever thought about saving them?

28:48.440 --> 28:49.570
Fate is already set.

28:49.920 --> 28:51.050
It cannot be forced.

28:51.160 --> 28:53.310
But where there is feeling,
there will be the urge to force it.

28:53.310 --> 28:54.880
Since you've never had emotions,

28:54.880 --> 28:55.550
how could you understand

28:55.550 --> 28:58.010
what "the great path is emotionless"
means?

29:00.750 --> 29:02.480
If you think I'm your "emotion"

29:02.790 --> 29:04.120
or your "tribulation",

29:04.490 --> 29:05.480
then your idea of "emotion"

29:05.480 --> 29:06.480
is far too narrow.

29:07.550 --> 29:09.210
You clearly know everything.

29:09.640 --> 29:11.440
You can see the suffering of this world

29:11.440 --> 29:13.150
and hear the cries of misery everywhere.

29:13.150 --> 29:13.920
You have the power and ability

29:13.920 --> 29:15.310
to change all this—

29:16.960 --> 29:19.020
yet you sit aloof on your lofty perch,

29:19.400 --> 29:20.680
watching coldly,

29:21.240 --> 29:22.720
and call it fate.

29:24.270 --> 29:25.600
This is not some "path."

29:26.830 --> 29:27.760
It's hypocrisy!

29:29.030 --> 29:30.430
You may appear merciful,

29:30.640 --> 29:33.070
but in truth,
you are cold-blooded and heartless.

29:33.070 --> 29:34.160
You cannot even resolve

29:34.160 --> 29:35.200
the suffering right before your eyes,

29:35.200 --> 29:37.000
yet you claim you want to save me?

29:40.000 --> 29:41.660
I'm warning you one last time—

29:42.550 --> 29:43.640
stop following me.

30:12.630 --> 30:14.030
You may appear merciful,

30:14.200 --> 30:16.640
but in truth,
you are cold-blooded and heartless.

30:16.640 --> 30:17.640
You cannot even resolve

30:17.640 --> 30:18.830
the suffering right before your eyes,

30:18.830 --> 30:20.630
yet you claim you want to save me?

30:21.030 --> 30:22.360
This is not some "path."

30:23.240 --> 30:24.170
It's hypocrisy!

30:25.480 --> 30:27.070
♪ I believe Heaven sees all ♪

30:27.090 --> 30:29.360
♪ Its wrath shines upon demons ♪

30:29.470 --> 30:32.850
♪ But who will show me mercy? ♪

30:33.020 --> 30:34.530
♪ I believe I'm innocent ♪

30:34.560 --> 30:39.860
♪ Turned into dust and scattered away ♪

30:40.610 --> 30:42.190
♪ I accept the blame of
numerous accusations ♪

30:42.210 --> 30:44.670
♪ I offer no defense ♪

30:44.700 --> 30:48.180
♪ I accept this as my only choice ♪

30:48.200 --> 30:51.230
♪ I accept this trial of love
fate has given me ♪

30:51.250 --> 30:56.190
♪ I take in both love and hate alike ♪

31:01.310 --> 31:02.110
Master.

31:03.030 --> 31:03.550
Master?

31:06.750 --> 31:07.590
Master!

31:09.880 --> 31:10.720
Master.

31:11.270 --> 31:12.240
Master!

31:14.200 --> 31:15.550
I'm here.

31:18.880 --> 31:19.440
Master.

31:19.750 --> 31:20.920
A letter has arrived from
Chongling Valley,

31:20.920 --> 31:22.640
saying the Immortality Pill
is about to be completed.

31:22.640 --> 31:23.110
Master,

31:23.350 --> 31:24.280
you can be saved.

31:26.510 --> 31:27.840
When are we setting off?

31:28.110 --> 31:28.840
Setting off?

31:29.030 --> 31:29.750
Where to?

31:30.270 --> 31:31.470
To Chongling Valley.

31:31.680 --> 31:33.310
Master, your time is almost up,

31:33.310 --> 31:34.880
and the Immortality Pill
happens to be almost ready.

31:34.880 --> 31:35.790
They can prolong your life

31:35.790 --> 31:36.750
and make you immortal.

31:36.750 --> 31:37.810
This is great news.

31:38.680 --> 31:39.610
We're not going.

31:40.000 --> 31:40.680
Why?

31:42.960 --> 31:44.160
I lost my jade tablet.

31:44.680 --> 31:46.240
It was hidden in the chicken coop.

31:46.240 --> 31:47.070
I found it.

31:47.560 --> 31:48.830
I haven't been feeling well
these past few days.

31:48.830 --> 31:49.560
I can't walk.

31:50.110 --> 31:50.960
Perfect timing.

31:50.960 --> 31:52.240
Chongling Valley has plenty of doctors.

31:52.240 --> 31:53.840
They can treat your illness.

31:54.640 --> 31:56.440
Anyway, we are simply not going.

31:57.200 --> 31:57.960
Why?

31:58.310 --> 32:00.510
Master, don't you want to live forever?

32:02.790 --> 32:03.520
My disciple,

32:03.680 --> 32:05.440
do you like the sun?

32:05.750 --> 32:07.350
Master, it's the wine talking again.

32:07.350 --> 32:09.240
Just tell me whether you like it or not.

32:09.240 --> 32:10.040
Of course I do.

32:10.400 --> 32:11.960
Its light nourishes all things

32:11.960 --> 32:12.960
and shines upon every corner.

32:12.960 --> 32:15.360
Everything in the world
lives by its grace.

32:16.870 --> 32:18.310
What if the sun

32:18.440 --> 32:20.310
stayed in the sky forever?

32:22.110 --> 32:22.960
Forever?

32:24.110 --> 32:25.770
All things must come to an end.

32:26.110 --> 32:28.110
Only when the sun sets can the moon rise.

32:28.110 --> 32:29.890
As I walk down the mountain,

32:29.920 --> 32:31.480
others will walk up.

32:32.680 --> 32:35.010
My disciple, you still have much to learn.

32:47.310 --> 32:49.030
As I walk down the mountain,

32:49.110 --> 32:50.590
others will walk up.

32:51.960 --> 32:54.290
My disciple, you still have much to learn.

32:55.400 --> 32:57.070
Immortal Xin, do you want this?

32:57.070 --> 32:59.350
Where did you get this
Gongshan Jade Tablet?

32:59.350 --> 33:00.350
I've only got this one piece.

33:00.350 --> 33:01.550
I wanted to sell it for a high price,

33:01.550 --> 33:02.880
but I heard yours had been stolen.

33:02.880 --> 33:03.750
Since we have a good relationship,

33:03.750 --> 33:04.680
I thought I'd offer it to you first.

33:04.680 --> 33:05.640
The price is negotiable.

33:05.640 --> 33:06.700
Do you know what the Gongshan Jade Tablet

33:06.700 --> 33:07.450
is for?

33:07.880 --> 33:08.790
Of course I do.

33:09.240 --> 33:10.030
To exchange for the Immortality Pill,

33:10.030 --> 33:10.960
to live forever.

33:11.270 --> 33:13.270
Then why are you selling it for money?

33:13.270 --> 33:14.830
The Immortality Pill is a divine medicine.

33:14.830 --> 33:15.880
Your immortal sects don't even
have enough for yourselves.

33:15.880 --> 33:17.160
How could I ever get a share?

33:17.160 --> 33:18.360
Besides, I'm so poor—

33:18.720 --> 33:21.180
what's the point of
living that long anyway?

33:22.590 --> 33:23.400
In fact,

33:24.440 --> 33:26.750
there's a small problem with
this jade tablet.

33:26.750 --> 33:27.270
Let me see it.

33:27.270 --> 33:29.070
Tell me if you're buying it first.

33:29.070 --> 33:30.130
Let me see it first.

33:33.110 --> 33:34.440
This is not a Gongshan Jade Tablet.

33:34.440 --> 33:36.440
How is it not a Gongshan Jade Tablet?

33:36.640 --> 33:37.680
Legend has it that
to prevent these jade tablets

33:37.680 --> 33:39.270
from being forged, Divine Doctor Su

33:39.270 --> 33:40.960
specially obtained a piece of

33:41.030 --> 33:42.440
ancient sinking jade from Gongshan.

33:42.440 --> 33:43.000
This jade

33:43.310 --> 33:45.310
is smooth and warm,
with crystal-clear essence.

33:45.310 --> 33:47.510
There's definitely no second piece
like it in this world.

33:47.510 --> 33:49.110
After making 30 jade tablets,

33:49.110 --> 33:50.350
there were some leftover scraps

33:50.350 --> 33:51.960
that got tossed into the back mountain,

33:51.960 --> 33:53.350
and I happened to pick them up.

33:53.350 --> 33:54.550
The materials were limited,

33:54.550 --> 33:55.610
so it's a bit small,

33:55.880 --> 33:57.830
but there are definitely
no quality problems.

33:57.830 --> 33:59.000
So you do know it's small.

33:59.000 --> 34:00.070
The size is different, for starters.

34:00.070 --> 34:02.270
As long as the material's the same,
it's fine, right?

34:02.270 --> 34:03.310
Besides, everyone knows

34:03.310 --> 34:04.350
you have one.

34:04.750 --> 34:05.880
So if you take this fake one,

34:05.880 --> 34:07.410
no one will suspect a thing.

34:08.800 --> 34:09.480
100 taels.

34:10.120 --> 34:11.199
100 taels for

34:11.230 --> 34:12.630
a chance at immortality—

34:12.710 --> 34:13.710
it can't be a loss.

34:14.150 --> 34:15.070
How many more do you have?

34:15.070 --> 34:15.929
I want them all.

34:16.030 --> 34:17.159
Just this one piece.

34:17.960 --> 34:19.840
This matter is not as simple as you think.

34:19.840 --> 34:21.360
You hang around Chongling Valley all day.

34:21.360 --> 34:22.489
You should know that

34:22.670 --> 34:23.780
someone has already died because of this.

34:23.780 --> 34:24.639
You are a mortal

34:24.810 --> 34:25.610
with no magic,

34:25.630 --> 34:26.860
yet you possess a great treasure.

34:26.860 --> 34:28.540
It's inevitable to attract greedy wolves.

34:28.540 --> 34:29.480
Be careful, or in the end,

34:29.480 --> 34:31.960
you may not gain the fortune you seek,
but instead lose your life.

34:31.960 --> 34:32.670
It's not like that. I...

34:32.670 --> 34:33.870
This is the last time.

34:34.230 --> 34:35.630
Don't sell this anymore.

34:37.510 --> 34:37.800
But

34:37.800 --> 34:38.860
the Gongshan Jade Tablet
is a piece of jade after all.

34:38.860 --> 34:41.520
It can't be worth
less than even one tael, can it?

34:41.960 --> 34:45.219
You said so much just because
you didn't want to pay, right?

34:54.219 --> 34:55.020
You're saying

34:55.400 --> 34:57.510
the magical artifact she used
is similar to mine?

34:57.510 --> 34:57.960
Yes.

34:58.800 --> 35:00.440
She usually uses a machete.

35:00.670 --> 35:02.000
When wielded by spiritual energy,

35:02.000 --> 35:02.710
it transforms into

35:02.710 --> 35:04.320
a moonlight-like magical artifact,

35:04.320 --> 35:06.050
which is exceptionally sharp.

35:25.920 --> 35:26.580
Senior Bai.

35:27.590 --> 35:28.720
What a coincidence.

35:28.800 --> 35:30.070
It's not a coincidence.

35:30.070 --> 35:31.270
I was waiting for you.

35:37.400 --> 35:39.590
Junior, you should recognize
this magical artifact.

35:39.590 --> 35:41.800
Back then, our Grandmaster traveled through
the wildlands of Cangwu

35:41.800 --> 35:42.780
and, with his profound skills,

35:42.780 --> 35:44.480
he slew the Sun-Moon Two-Headed Beast.

35:44.480 --> 35:45.840
That demon had a bird's head
and a serpent's tail,

35:45.840 --> 35:47.550
two heads on one body,
and wings on its ribs.

35:47.550 --> 35:48.840
Its feathers were dazzling—

35:48.840 --> 35:50.590
half blazing like the sun,

35:50.880 --> 35:52.510
the other half pure and bright
like the moon.

35:52.510 --> 35:53.910
Our Grandmaster slew it,

35:53.920 --> 35:55.760
took its core, plucked its feathers,

35:55.760 --> 35:57.070
and refined them through secret methods.

35:57.070 --> 35:58.840
In the end, he forged 2 magical artifacts:

35:58.840 --> 36:00.480
the Sun Splendor and the Moon Splendor.

36:00.480 --> 36:01.760
I inherited the Sun Splendor

36:01.760 --> 36:03.150
from my master.

36:03.800 --> 36:05.960
Junior, as the eldest disciple
of Xin Xie Manor,

36:05.960 --> 36:06.960
did Senior Uncle

36:07.710 --> 36:09.640
pass the Moon Splendor down to you?

36:18.510 --> 36:20.310
It is indeed as bright as the moon

36:20.360 --> 36:21.620
and as cold as the wind.

36:22.760 --> 36:23.480
Senior,

36:24.000 --> 36:25.840
what exactly are you trying to say?

36:25.840 --> 36:26.770
Half a month ago,

36:27.110 --> 36:29.070
an odd incident took place in the capital.

36:29.070 --> 36:30.220
To avenge her husband,

36:30.220 --> 36:31.330
a female cultivator surnamed Xin

36:31.330 --> 36:32.070
killed 4 court officials

36:32.070 --> 36:33.070
in succession.

36:33.800 --> 36:35.670
Afterward, even under a joint manhunt
by the immortal sects,

36:35.670 --> 36:37.480
she still managed to leave unscathed.

36:37.480 --> 36:38.930
A friend of mine who saw her said

36:38.930 --> 36:39.640
she used

36:39.670 --> 36:41.670
a moonlight magical artifact
similar to mine.

36:41.670 --> 36:42.600
I'd like to know—

36:43.190 --> 36:44.710
was that female cultivator in the capital

36:44.710 --> 36:45.550
you, Junior?

36:46.440 --> 36:47.170
It wasn't me.

36:47.960 --> 36:49.760
I have never been to the capital.

36:51.050 --> 36:51.730
Junior, you

36:51.760 --> 36:53.320
left your sect a long time ago,

36:53.320 --> 36:55.000
yet you only arrived at Chongling Valley
a few days ago.

36:55.000 --> 36:57.260
How could the journey have taken so long?

36:58.230 --> 37:00.030
I made a trip back to my hometown.

37:00.150 --> 37:02.210
I originally wanted to visit my aunt,

37:02.440 --> 37:03.510
but when I got back,

37:03.710 --> 37:05.910
I found out she had already passed away.

37:05.920 --> 37:07.110
So I stayed in Wei County

37:07.110 --> 37:08.840
to handle her funeral affairs.

37:08.840 --> 37:10.670
Later, due to excessive grief

37:11.150 --> 37:12.920
and getting caught in the rain
along the way,

37:12.920 --> 37:14.180
I fell ill and fainted.

37:14.510 --> 37:15.070
Fortunately,

37:15.070 --> 37:16.470
a kind landlady saved me,

37:16.960 --> 37:18.960
and I stayed at the inn
for a few extra days.

37:18.960 --> 37:21.560
That's why I arrived late
at Chongling Valley.

37:25.710 --> 37:27.220
If you don't believe me, Senior,

37:27.220 --> 37:28.590
you can go to Safe Haven Inn
at Wuli Slope

37:28.590 --> 37:30.520
outside Wei County and ask around.

37:30.980 --> 37:32.320
The landlady and the staff there

37:32.320 --> 37:33.450
can all vouch for me.

37:35.110 --> 37:35.910
I believe you.

37:36.230 --> 37:37.440
Since you said so, Junior,

37:37.440 --> 37:38.770
of course I believe you.

37:40.400 --> 37:41.230
Besides,

37:42.550 --> 37:43.840
I'm not yet married,

37:44.590 --> 37:46.050
and I don't have a husband.

37:47.150 --> 37:48.750
That was presumptuous of me.

37:50.830 --> 37:52.230
Sorry for bothering you for so long.

37:52.230 --> 37:53.290
I should leave now.

37:54.110 --> 37:55.370
Wait a minute, Senior.

38:03.780 --> 38:06.030
You brought me delicacies
from my hometown.

38:06.030 --> 38:07.190
The food is precious,

38:07.190 --> 38:08.920
but your kindness is even more so.

38:08.920 --> 38:09.630
I truly don't know

38:09.630 --> 38:10.830
how to repay you.

38:11.510 --> 38:14.170
Please accept this fragrance pendant
as a gift.

38:16.070 --> 38:17.150
I made it myself.

38:17.590 --> 38:18.650
It's made of ebony,

38:18.710 --> 38:20.230
has a delicate, subtle scent,

38:20.230 --> 38:22.360
and can repel insects and mosquitoes.

38:25.070 --> 38:26.130
Thank you, Junior.

38:40.190 --> 38:40.990
Grandmaster.

38:59.630 --> 39:00.230
Master.

39:00.630 --> 39:01.830
Grandmaster is back.

39:10.710 --> 39:11.510
Miss Xin.

39:38.090 --> 39:40.530
[Clear Sky, Fresh Air]

40:06.360 --> 40:08.220
They brought it upon themselves.

40:09.590 --> 40:11.480
You once told me, Master,

40:11.890 --> 40:13.180
that in this world there are broad paths

40:13.180 --> 40:14.240
and narrow trails.

40:14.590 --> 40:16.780
The broad paths are easy to travel,
while the narrow trails are difficult.

40:16.780 --> 40:18.260
Yet what people seek

40:18.320 --> 40:20.720
most often lies along those narrow trails.

40:21.280 --> 40:21.960
Therefore,

40:22.360 --> 40:23.760
if they want to get through,

40:23.760 --> 40:25.960
they have to risk their flesh and blood,

40:25.960 --> 40:27.590
suffer broken bones,

40:27.840 --> 40:29.500
and get bruised and battered.

40:31.920 --> 40:34.080
That's driven by human greed.

40:35.000 --> 40:37.030
What does it have to do with me?

40:57.870 --> 40:59.000
I taught you medicine

40:59.000 --> 41:00.400
so you could make a living

41:00.550 --> 41:01.410
and save lives.

41:01.670 --> 41:03.070
I taught you the principles of
being a decent person

41:03.070 --> 41:04.760
so you could grow into someone
of integrity and ability,

41:04.760 --> 41:06.570
not so you could twist words
to evade guilt!

41:06.570 --> 41:07.760
You say that those who seek immortality

41:07.760 --> 41:09.620
are all walking the narrow trail.

41:09.630 --> 41:10.410
Then tell me—

41:10.760 --> 41:11.970
what about those ordinary people?

41:11.970 --> 41:12.880
Why should they lose their lives

41:12.880 --> 41:14.150
for your pursuit of immortality?

41:14.150 --> 41:15.480
Is everything they seek

41:15.590 --> 41:16.800
also on that narrow trail?
